Unconcerned with the unsightly behaviour neighbours were subjected to, the men spent the warm day engaged in a public display of inappropriateness.

Their 'tour' started with the men converging on their bicycles at one participant’s house, where they poured wine from a cask into one anothers mouths.

At another early point in their tour, a smaller group of men can be seen pouring beer onto one participant’s hairy breasts and drinking it from his bare skin.

