As the day progressed, some of the men began removing their clothing and jumping into swimming pools.

Being so intoxicated that they were vomiting wasn’t even enough to deter some of them – merely serving as an opportunity to empty their stomachs so they could drink more.

It might seem like harmless fun to some, but the group appear to be showing no concern for the safety of local residents who may have come across the group.

