Converging at a skateboarding park, intended for residents of the community to enjoy during the daytime – the men continued to put themselves at risk by jumping on tour participants as they attempted to perform bicycle tricks.

Even potentially getting an infringement from police wasn’t enough to deter some of the rowdy revellers – with some participants continuing to drink alcohol during the ride on to the next house.   

MailOnline has sought comment from Western Australia Police and the City of Swan Council.

